---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Bitsec" description="Read Bitsec Digital Agency's privacy policy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-32">

    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-text-primary dark:text-white mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary dark:text-gray-400 mb-10">Last updated: March 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-10 text-text-secondary dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary dark:text-white mb-3">1. What We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you fill out our contact form, we collect your name, email address, phone number, and your message. We may also automatically collect basic analytics data such as browser type and country code when you visit our site.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary dark:text-white mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information you provide solely to get in touch with you and deliver the services you requested. We never sell, rent, or share your personal data with any third party.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary dark:text-white mb-3">3. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We take reasonable precautions to keep your information secure. Our systems go through regular security reviews. That said, no method of transmission over the internet is completely secure, so we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary dark:text-white mb-3">4. Cookies</h2>
        <p>Our website may use essential cookies to improve site functionality. You can disable cookies at any time through your browser settings, though some features may not work as expected if you do.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary dark:text-white mb-3">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We may use third-party analytics tools like Google Analytics to understand how visitors use our site. These tools operate under their own privacy policies.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary dark:text-white mb-3">6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You can request to view, correct, or delete any personal information we hold about you at any time. Just reach out to us at:</p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          <a href="mailto:helpline.bitsec@gmail.com" class="text-primary underline font-medium">helpline.bitsec@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary dark:text-white mb-3">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with a new date. Continued use of our site after changes means you accept the updated policy.</p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
